  <body>
    <div style="basic">
        <p begin="00:00:00.000" end="00:00:01.640" tts:direction="ltr">Hello, visitors.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:01.640" end="00:00:05.840" tts:direction="ltr">You have arrived at your very first base
<br />camp and I'm excited for you to</p>
        <p begin="00:00:05.840" end="00:00:10.240" tts:direction="ltr">learn about these concepts that are
<br />transferable to any application,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:10.240" end="00:00:14.200" tts:direction="ltr">not just Tableau, but Power BI, Excel,
<br />Domo,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:14.200" end="00:00:17.240" tts:direction="ltr">anything that the future might hold so
<br />that</p>
        <p begin="00:00:17.240" end="00:00:20.440" tts:direction="ltr">you can feel confident in your
<br />visualization skills.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:20.440" end="00:00:23.645" tts:direction="ltr">Let's take a look at your learning journey
<br />map.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:23.645" end="00:00:26.450" tts:direction="ltr">And you've done a great job by tackling</p>
        <p begin="00:00:26.450" end="00:00:30.770" tts:direction="ltr">your Tableau adventures and you've
<br />participated in your first Karen.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:30.770" end="00:00:34.970" tts:direction="ltr">Now we are at your very first base camp
<br />and that will</p>
        <p begin="00:00:34.970" end="00:00:40.130" tts:direction="ltr">cover these core principles of purpose,
<br />audience, and credibility.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:40.130" end="00:00:43.610" tts:direction="ltr">You're going to learn about PAC and you
<br />will have a chance to do</p>
        <p begin="00:00:43.610" end="00:00:48.490" tts:direction="ltr">a Data Talk so that you can think and
<br />write about a chart.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:48.490" end="00:00:51.850" tts:direction="ltr">You'll also have a chance to work on your
<br />very first challenge.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:51.850" end="00:00:54.290" tts:direction="ltr">This will be some Google trend data that
<br />you will</p>
        <p begin="00:00:54.290" end="00:00:57.025" tts:direction="ltr">download and then bring in Tableau</p>
        <p begin="00:00:57.025" end="00:00:59.240" tts:direction="ltr">and visualize your insights.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:59.240" end="00:01:01.120" tts:direction="ltr">In addition to those activities,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:01.120" end="00:01:02.960" tts:direction="ltr">here are the three objectives that you
<br />will</p>
        <p begin="00:01:02.960" end="00:01:05.000" tts:direction="ltr">have for this particular base camp.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:05.000" end="00:01:08.680" tts:direction="ltr">You're going to understand the importance
<br />of distilling a problem or</p>
        <p begin="00:01:08.680" end="00:01:12.680" tts:direction="ltr">a wonder into a single sentence, that
<br />single purpose.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:12.680" end="00:01:14.080" tts:direction="ltr">You're going to analyze</p>
        <p begin="00:01:14.080" end="00:01:17.895" tts:direction="ltr">different audiences to understand what
<br />they think, feel, and do.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:17.895" end="00:01:21.190" tts:direction="ltr">You will be synthesizing data as you
<br />extract</p>
        <p begin="00:01:21.190" end="00:01:25.270" tts:direction="ltr">key insights for that audience into your
<br />challenge,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:25.270" end="00:01:27.350" tts:direction="ltr">and then you should be able to explain</p>
        <p begin="00:01:27.350" end="00:01:29.990" tts:direction="ltr">those five data quality characteristics</p>
        <p begin="00:01:29.990" end="00:01:33.030" tts:direction="ltr">so that you can ensure that your data is
<br />always credible.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:33.030" end="00:01:37.070" tts:direction="ltr">I look forward to seeing your very first
<br />challenge and for you to learn</p>
        <p begin="00:01:37.070" end="00:01:39.830" tts:direction="ltr">these concepts because they are critical
<br />in</p>
        <p begin="00:01:39.830" end="00:01:43.870" tts:direction="ltr">communicating clearly to your audience.
<br />Happy visit.</p>
    </div>
